*.dmp

# NOTE:
# Prebuilt plugin libraries (*.a / *.lib) under Plugins/ are intentionally
# committed, so binary file extensions are NOT ignored globally. Build outputs
# are excluded via the folder rules above (Binaries/, Intermediate/, ...).
